(He's shaking so much.)

75
00:04:15,010 --> 00:04:15,530
What is that?

76
00:04:15,531 --> 00:04:16,770
(Is it the Soul Grass?)

77
00:04:16,771 --> 00:04:17,960
(Who has it?)

78
00:04:20,290 --> 00:04:21,241
He...

79
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:23,520
He has epilepsy.

80
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:24,489
Are you okay?

81
00:04:24,490 --> 00:04:25,729
He's suffering from a relapse.

82
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:27,809
Actually, we came
to Medicine King Valley

83
00:04:27,810 --> 00:04:28,970
to seek treatment

84
00:04:28,971 --> 00:04:30,121
for him.

85
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:32,369
Yes.

86
00:04:32,370 --> 00:04:33,330
I'm sick.

87
00:04:33,331 --> 00:04:34,600
Yeah, he's sick.

88
