90
00:04:48,170 --> 00:04:49,600
when we go outside.

91
00:04:49,690 --> 00:04:52,040
We brought it to ensure our safety.

92
00:04:58,571 --> 00:04:59,720
Miss Jiu,

93
00:05:00,531 --> 00:05:02,090
in Medicine King Valley,

94
00:05:02,091 --> 00:05:04,520
we don't need a gun
to resolve any issues.

95
00:05:04,651 --> 00:05:05,289
You should

96
00:05:05,290 --> 00:05:06,929
hand the gun to me.

97
00:05:06,930 --> 00:05:09,080
I'll return it to you
when you're leaving.

98
00:05:14,851 --> 00:05:17,121
Why did you make him
pretend to be my master?

99
00:05:17,490 --> 00:05:19,049
The design of the necklace,

100
00:05:19,050 --> 00:05:20,770
even the design of the outfit,

101
00:05:20,771 --> 00:05:22,681
they look just like my master's.

102
00:05:25,211 --> 00:05:27,080
So, Ma Gu is your master?

103
00:05:33,651 --> 00:05:34,929
So, you're the martial uncle

104
00:05:34,930 --> 00:05:36,720
my master had mentioned to me?

105
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:40,121
You were the one who stood idly by
when my master died,

106
00:05:40,531 --> 00:05:41,840
right?

107
00:05:48,891 --> 00:05:50,681
I've let your master down.

108
00:05:51,050 --> 00:05:51,570
Jingtian.

109
00:05:51,571 --> 00:05:53,520
I've let Ma Gu down!

110
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:54,720
Jingtian.

111
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:56,201
I've let her down...

112
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:05,681
This is the new prescription
I have invented.

113
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:09,921
That's great.

114
00:06:13,891 --> 00:06:14,890
This is for you.

115
00:06:14,891 --> 00:06:16,121
It's for me?

116
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:20,200
- But I never expected scheming people
- It looks great.

117
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,441
- to target her prescriptions.
- You're so nice to me.

118
00:06:22,451 --> 00:06:23,809
They hired some thugs.

119
00:06:23,810 --> 00:06:25,489
Shi Jingtian, come out!

120
00:06:25,490 --> 00:06:26,570
Shi Jingtian, come out!

121
00:06:26,571 --> 00:06:28,330
- Shi Jingtian!
- Shi Jingtian! Come out!

122
00:06:28,331 --> 00:06:29,040
Come out!

123
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:30,530
- Don't open it.
- Open the door!

124
00:06:30,531 --> 00:06:32,240
It's obvious that they're framing you!

125
00:06:32,241 --> 00:06:32,970
Shi Jingtian!

126
00:06:32,971 --> 00:06:34,729
- Shi. Open the door!
- Shi Jingtian, come out!

127
00:06:34,730 --> 00:06:35,450
I'll go outside

128
00:06:35,451 --> 00:06:36,289
and reason with them!

129
00:06:36,290 --> 00:06:38,600
- Shi Jingtian, open the door!
- Hurry and come out!

130
00:06:39,290 --> 00:06:41,650
Ma Gu, just ignore them.
They're upset right now.

131
00:06:41,651 --> 00:06:42,330
If you go outside,

132
00:06:42,331 --> 00:06:43,920
- you'll be at a disadvantage.
- Come out!

133
00:06:43,971 --> 00:06:44,689
What about this?

134
00:06:44,690 --> 00:06:45,410
Just let them be.

135
00:06:45,411 --> 00:06:46,570
They'll run out of energy.

136
00:06:46,571 --> 00:06:47,840
Wait for them to leave.

137
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:49,609
Shi, we can't let them be.

138
00:06:49,610 --> 00:06:51,650
If they keep doing this,

139
00:06:51,651 --> 00:06:52,809
you won't be able

140
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:54,321
to operate your herb store!

141
00:06:54,571 --> 00:06:55,561
Ma Gu!

142
00:06:55,571 --> 00:06:55,970
Come out!

143
00:06:55,971 --> 00:06:57,840
Stop maligning him!

144
00:06:57,851 --> 00:06:59,010
Come out if you're a man!

145
00:06:59,011 --> 00:07:00,441
Why are you guys trying to frame him?

146
00:07:00,531 --> 00:07:02,289
Who are you to him?

147
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:03,850
He sells spurious herbs!

148
00:07:03,851 --> 00:07:05,450
My father died after taking it!

149
00:07:05,451 --> 00:07:06,809
He's a murderer!

150
00:07:06,810 --> 00:07:08,320
What nonsense are you talking about?

151
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:10,720
Do you believe
that I'll report this to the authorities

152
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,040
and have you guys arrested?

153
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,040
Hurry and leave!

154
00:07:15,130 --> 00:07:17,450
You're Shi Jingtian's accomplice.

155
00:07:17,451 --> 00:07:19,480
Both of you are liars!

156
00:07:19,891 --> 00:07:21,689
Return my father to me!

157
00:07:21,690 --> 00:07:23,480
I'll kill you!

158
00:07:28,730 --> 00:07:29,720
Ma Gu!

159
00:07:29,730 --> 00:07:30,650
I!

160
00:07:30,651 --> 00:07:31,640
Go to hell!

161
00:07:35,490 --> 00:07:37,201
To hell with you!

162
00:07:38,651 --> 00:07:39,890
Shi Jingtian, come out!

163
00:07:39,891 --> 00:07:41,169
Open the door!

164
00:07:41,170 --> 00:07:42,570
Shi Jingtian!

165
00:07:42,571 --> 00:07:43,929
Come out!

166
