Shi, open the door!

169
00:07:54,571 --> 00:07:56,600
Save me!

170
00:07:59,370 --> 00:08:01,361
Hurry and come out!

171
00:08:02,483 --> 00:08:03,770
Darned wretch!

172
00:08:03,771 --> 00:08:05,600
How dare you obstruct us?

173
00:08:25,050 --> 00:08:26,400
Ma Gu...

174
00:08:27,011 --> 00:08:28,330
Since then,

175
00:08:28,331 --> 00:08:29,761
I was mentally distressed.

176
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:31,640
I had nightmares every night.

177
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:34,041
After that,

178
00:08:34,130 --> 00:08:35,720
I went to Medicine King Valley.

179
00:08:35,971 --> 00:08:37,290
I established this stone fort

180
00:08:37,291 --> 00:08:39,120
with the money I made
from her prescriptions.

181
00:08:39,691 --> 00:08:40,880
I spent a lot of money

182
00:08:41,051 --> 00:08:43,249
to place a hit on the three thugs.

183
00:08:43,250 --> 00:08:44,769
I turned them into wax corpses.

184
00:08:44,770 --> 00:08:46,129
I want them to kneel and apologize

185
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:48,201
to Ma Gu for all eternity.

186
00:08:50,051 --> 00:08:52,990
I even told my servants
to not close the door at night.

187
00:08:53,851 --> 00:08:56,480
I instruct them to light candles
at night to welcome her spirit.

188
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:01,561
Paper dolls weren't real enough.

189
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:05,120
They couldn't express my regret
toward Ma Gu.

190
00:09:07,091 --> 00:09:08,161
Therefore,

191
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:11,720
I bought real corpses
to worship the spirit of Ma Gu.

192
00:09:12,010 --> 00:09:13,649
I make them atone for my sin

193
00:09:13,650 --> 00:09:15,360
for eternity.

194
00:09:16,130 --> 00:09:17,441
Whenever Mr. Jingtian

195
00:09:17,571 --> 00:09:19,880
kneels in the hall every night,

196
00:09:20,250 --> 00:09:22,810
I have to pretend to be Ma Gu
and knock on the door.

197
00:09:22,811 --> 00:09:24,801
He can only close his eyes

198
00:09:25,291 --> 00:09:26,480
and sleep

199
00:09:26,650 --> 00:09:27,649
on that night

200
00:09:27,650 --> 00:09:28,930
when the door

201
00:09:28,931 --> 00:09:29,960
is opened.

202
00:09:31,130 --> 00:09:33,441
You shameless man.

203
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:35,609
Master died because of you!

204
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:37,880
Even so, you're still
putting on an act like this!

205
00:09:38,610 --> 00:09:41,080
You pretend to blame yourself
and act as if you're a devoted man.

206
00:09:41,291 --> 00:09:43,210
You truly disgust me.

207
00:09:43,211 --> 00:09:44,409
I've never seen

208
00:09:44,410 --> 00:09:46,521
a man as shameless as you.

209
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:48,801
I'm sorry.

210
00:09:48,811 --> 00:09:50,561
I'm sorry!

211
00:09:51,010 --> 00:09:52,240
Sorry?

212
00:09:52,331 --> 00:09:53,609
Do you think

213
00:09:53,610 --> 00:09:54,769
that will neutralize the harm

214
00:09:54,770 --> 00:09:56,521
you've done to her?

215
00:09:56,931 --> 00:09:58,210
Can I kill you

216
00:09:58,211 --> 00:10:00,161
if I say sorry to you?

217
00:10:00,530 --> 00:10:01,769
If I can,

218
00:10:01,770 --> 00:10:04,161
you better extend your neck
and let me chop it off.

219
00:10:04,691 --> 00:10:06,129
If not,

220
00:10:06,130 --> 00:10:07,489
what you said just now

221
00:10:07,490 --> 00:10:08,649
was full of nonsense!

222
00:10:08,650 --> 00:10:09,840
Miss Jiu.

223
00:10:10,730 --> 00:10:12,120
If you keep this up,

224
00:10:12,770 --> 00:10:14,489
I shall show you no mercy.

225
00:10:14,490 --> 00:10:16,321
I've let Ma Gu down.

226
00:10:16,451 --> 00:10:17,760
It's all my fault!

227
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:24,600
Jingtian!

228
00:10:24,691 --> 00:10:25,690
Ma Gu, I'm sorry!

229
00:10:25,691 --> 00:10:27,170
Ma Gu, where are you?

230
00:10:27,171 --> 00:10:27,529
Ma Gu!

231
00:10:27,530 --> 00:10:28,290
Mr. Jingtian!

232
00:10:28,291 --> 00:10:29,889
- Don't kill me!
- Jingtian!

233
00:10:29,890 --> 00:10:30,529
