234
00:10:30,530 --> 00:10:30,889
Jingtian!

235
00:10:30,890 --> 00:10:31,369
Ma Gu!

236
00:10:31,370 --> 00:10:32,249
Mr. Jingtian!

237
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:33,009
Ma Gu!

238
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:33,489
Ma Gu!

239
00:10:33,490 --> 00:10:34,561
Mr. Jingtian!

240
00:10:35,051 --> 00:10:36,769
Ma Gu, where are you?

241
00:10:36,770 --> 00:10:39,129
I'm begging you!

242
00:10:39,130 --> 00:10:40,930
- Please don't kill me!
- Mr. Jingtian!

243
00:10:40,931 --> 00:10:42,561
Ma Gu!

244
00:10:42,571 --> 00:10:45,240
- Just kill me!
- Hurry and call for the witch doctor!

245
00:10:47,851 --> 00:10:49,050
Jingtian, it's fine.

246
00:10:49,051 --> 00:10:50,360
I'm here for you.

247
00:10:51,971 --> 00:10:52,930
Jingtian, it's fine.

248
00:10:52,931 --> 00:10:54,120
I'm here for you.

249
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:59,529
My senior is suffering from a relapse.

250
00:10:59,530 --> 00:11:01,041
He needs to rest and recuperate.

251
00:11:01,091 --> 00:11:02,960
The three of you shouldn't stay here.

252
00:11:03,331 --> 00:11:04,720
You guys should head back first.

253
00:11:09,530 --> 00:11:12,080
When Shi Jingtian's ailment
was acting up,

254
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:13,201
the Yin Sting Bug

255
00:11:13,291 --> 00:11:14,840
ruptured and died.

256
00:11:16,610 --> 00:11:18,170
Shi Jingtian

257
00:11:18,171 --> 00:11:19,801
must be closely related

258
00:11:19,851 --> 00:11:21,840
to the Soul Grass.

259
00:11:23,130 --> 00:11:25,450
Is there any way we can obtain
another Yin Sting Bug?

260
00:11:25,451 --> 00:11:26,210
I think

261
00:11:26,211 --> 00:11:27,570
we can give it one more try.

262
00:11:27,571 --> 00:11:28,450
Oh please.

263
00:11:28,451 --> 00:11:29,970
It's a Yin Sting Bug.

264
00:11:29,971 --> 00:11:31,921
It'll take at least
one year to create it.

265
00:11:42,010 --> 00:11:43,889
